column5: Do u think William and Harry were sing : " God save my grandmummy" ?
Pass the gin and tonic! HH
I think hereditary succession is horrible.  Yuck.
she's hot...I mean Kate, not the queen...or do I?

I've had this debate with my family over the past few weeks.  Why does anyone still care about monarchs?  I understand that Canada is a dominion of Britain, but really how has the royal family impacted our lives as Canadians other than the occasional, obligatory visit?  Maybe it's a generational thing, but I couldn't care less about two strangers getting married.
I agree 100%. I'm so sick of hearing about anything to do with anyone in that family! Who cares if they got married, or if it fails in a year. i
You think? In some pics she does look hot and then in others she looks, well, less hot. I cannot make up my mind if she's hot or not
I know I don't care, in fact to care less would require effort I'm not willing to give!  It's almost the weekend, get set and go fishing.
